*radiant-0.9.1 (29 Jul 2010)

  29 Jul 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +radiant-0.9.1.ebuild:
  Version bump.

*radiant-0.8.2-r1 (01 Jun 2010)

  01 Jun 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +radiant-0.8.2-r1.ebuild,
  +files/radiant-0.8.2-migration.patch:
  Convert to ruby-fakegem. Remove some vendored packages and make them
  external dependencies instead.

*radiant-0.8.2 (01 May 2010)

  01 May 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +radiant-0.8.2.ebuild:
  Version bump: allow tasks to run when higher version of cucumber is
  installed.

  14 Sep 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -radiant-0.7.1.ebuild,
  -radiant-0.8.0.ebuild:
  Remove old versions with vulnerable Rails versions included.

